      <div class="msgContentFrame">The gear damage / repair system in this game is a poorly thought out / poorly executed attempt by the devs to be &quot;innovative&quot;. <br /> <br />No other game forces the player to &quot;run through hoops&quot;, just to keep their gear in optimum condition. <br />  <br /> <br /></div>
